- `npm run deploy` - Deploy to gh-pages

## Key Libraries Usage

### Motion (Framer Motion)
- Import: `import * as motion from "motion/react-client"`
- Use for scroll animations, page transitions
- Client component required (use "use client" if needed)

### React Icons
- Import from specific icon sets: `react-icons/fa`, `react-icons/si`, etc.
- Use in components with size and color props

### Next.js Image
- Always use `next/image` instead of `<img>`
- Provides automatic optimization
- Requires width/height or fill prop

